quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  37,25,"Ko he…ďi on, on wallindirtaa"
  37,26,"Ko woni kam…ďe on hannde, ko …ďe jebbilii …ďe"
  37,27,"wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe fewtita …ďeya, …ďe lamndondira"
  37,28,"…ďe wi'a: \"Ko onon woni ko ardiranaynoo men, ka …ďaŇčŇče √Īaamo"
  37,29,"(Koohoo…ďe) …ďen wi'a: \"Ko woni kon, on mee…óaano wonnde gom…óim…ďe"
  37,30,"Doole woo men alanaano on. Si ko woni, on wonuno yim…ďe bew…ďe"
  37,31,"Konngol Joomi men ngol, jojjii e men; pellet, ko en mee…óoo…ďe [lepte …óen]"
  37,32,"Men bewinno on, tawde hay menen, ko men bewnoo…ďe"
  37,33,"Kam…ďe on nden √Īalnde, ko …ďe hawtoytee…ďe ka lepte"
  37,34,Ko nii Menen Men huuwirta bom…ďe …ďen
  37,35,"Kam…ďe si …ďe wi'anooma: \"Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Alla\", …ďe mawnintinoo"
  37,36,"…ďe wi'a: \"Kere men accitiray rewetee…ói amen …óin, fii yimoowo haangaa…óo"
  37,37,"Si ko woni, (Nulaa…óo) on ko goonga ardi, o goongini Nulaa…ďe …ďen"
  37,38,"Pellet, ko on mee…óay …ďe lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  37,39,"On yo…ďitetaake, si wanaa yeru kon ko huuwayno…óon"
  37,40,si wanaa jeyaa…ďe Alla la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen
  37,41,"hino woodani …ďen …óon, fanndaari anndaandi"
  37,42,"muuyantee…ói, kadi ko …ďe teddinaa…ďe"
  37,43,ka Aljannaaji neeminii…ói
  37,44,"e hoore dan…óe, ko …ďe fewtondir…ďe"
  37,45,"Hara kore hino wannginii e ma…ď…ďe, immorde e …ďulirde"
  37,46,"daneere, lew√Īunde, fii yaroo…ďe"
  37,47,"muusu hoore alaa e majjam, wanaa …óam siwrinirtee…ďe …óam"
  37,48,"Hino woodani …ďe (ton): ra…ď…ďidu…ďe ndaar…óe, yaaja gitee…ďe"
  37,49,wa'u…ďe wa boofo maraa…óe
  37,50,"Wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe fewtita …ďeya, …ďe lamndondira"
  37,51,"Go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe wi'a: \"Min mi…óo marunoo wonndii…óo"
